This is to show even if you add __init__.py to the top folder and the subfolders in it, still you will
run into this confusing error: ValueError: Attempted relative import in non-package, when your run a 
script directory in the folder

In this case, if you cd to the subpackage1, and run python ./module_x.py you will the above error.



